  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Goal:</strong> Guide <strong>Kubke</strong> in his search of <strong>6 Elemental Orbs</strong>, build the <strong>City of Elements</strong> and face the keeper of all knowledge, <strong>Yazik</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560170/extras/3527243c006ca6e1f6502964f24eb94d.poster.avif?t=1742284804\" width=500 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560170/extras/3527243c006ca6e1f6502964f24eb94d.webm?t=1742284804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560170/extras/3527243c006ca6e1f6502964f24eb94d.mp4?t=1742284804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your own Golem:</strong> Construct a powerful Adventure Golem to explore a procedurally generated hexagonal world for you. Upgrade it to take on more powerful foes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hexagonal Research Puzzle Minigame:</strong> Study and connect elemental aspects in order to conduct research. As you progress, the minigame will become more challenging, but the rewards will be better too!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Resource Management:</strong> Divide up your golem workforce between tasks so that the City of Elements prospers even when you are not watching.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore the world of Yagazem with its own language:</strong> Read about the lore of a fantasy world. Learn how to pronounce the word using a built-in orthography chart.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560170/extras/4e7da44ac6d32b303ec2694f2727c20c.poster.avif?t=1742284804\" width=514 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560170/extras/4e7da44ac6d32b303ec2694f2727c20c.webm?t=1742284804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560170/extras/4e7da44ac6d32b303ec2694f2727c20c.mp4?t=1742284804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Goal:</strong> Guide <strong>Kubke</strong> in his search of <strong>6 Elemental Orbs</strong>, build the <strong>City of Elements</strong> and face the keeper of all knowledge, <strong>Yazik</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560170/extras/3527243c006ca6e1f6502964f24eb94d.poster.avif?t=1742284804\" width=500 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560170/extras/3527243c006ca6e1f6502964f24eb94d.webm?t=1742284804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560170/extras/3527243c006ca6e1f6502964f24eb94d.mp4?t=1742284804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your own Golem:</strong> Construct a powerful Adventure Golem to explore a procedurally generated hexagonal world for you. Upgrade it to take on more powerful foes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hexagonal Research Puzzle Minigame:</strong> Study and connect elemental aspects in order to conduct research. As you progress, the minigame will become more challenging, but the rewards will be better too!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Resource Management:</strong> Divide up your golem workforce between tasks so that the City of Elements prospers even when you are not watching.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore the world of Yagazem with its own language:</strong> Read about the lore of a fantasy world. Learn how to pronounce the word using a built-in orthography chart.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560170/extras/4e7da44ac6d32b303ec2694f2727c20c.poster.avif?t=1742284804\" width=514 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560170/extras/4e7da44ac6d32b303ec2694f2727c20c.webm?t=1742284804\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560170/extras/4e7da44ac6d32b303ec2694f2727c20c.mp4?t=1742284804\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
